{"tid":278460,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[美服巨商] The Great Merchant 新人事新作風 #4","createTime":"2017-06-10T12:56:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T12:13:52.000Z","uid":59060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b76adf82a86c19b91df80851abd461fd91177c2","tid":278460,"uid":59060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T12:56:55.000Z","msg":"巨商呢隻GAME 唔洗咁多介紹啦<br />\n由爛橙到普雷威 都十年有多 仲要受代理無限CAMP水抽封書?<br />\n想完夢? 想合神? 合天王? 美服幫到你<br />\n想輕鬆玩? 課金玩? 柒住玩? 都得<br />\n官網: <a href=\"http://www.thegreatmerchant.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thegreatmerchant.com&d=P7KVl3aCdbmW02rc9LcTz7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=e82ee13b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.thegreatmerchant.com</a><br />\n本團RC: 27651903<br />\n其他香港團RC/團<br />\nWFC: 未知<br />\nFoReVeR: 未知<br />\n<br />\n1.新手難唔難起手?<br />\n本團與同其他大團合作攻城, 新手賺錢比其他團快. 合神冇難度啦<br />\n<br />\n2.點品貴唔貴? 封書又幾錢?<br />\n點品 USD 5= 5000GP = 封書封珠 市價約 170-180M 不等(GP格價與市場需求而變動, 課金前請三思)<br />\n<br />\n3. 多唔多外掛?<br />\n美服 外掛唔算多(未影響到市場) GM以前捉掛手法令人喪膽 換左GM ON99<br />\n<br />\n4.美巨以咩人流為主?<br />\n主要以印尼, 台灣, 香港, 大陸等等<br />\n<br />\n5.合神合馬難唔難?<br />\n本團內有大量廠主 消牌 合神 冇難度, 更有大量升LV 變態佬在<br />\n<br />\n注意本團不歡迎 叫春 派膠 如有發現"},{"pid":"0f16be382b18290635908e6598c2b26f5470f77b","tid":278460,"uid":49771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T13:01:05.000Z","msg":"頭香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0582962de81975a2bf9ff8c5690ae7458f0ba6c9","tid":278460,"uid":59060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T13:34:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae79ce86a63d3602d72a532fa596cfa890b735a6","tid":278460,"uid":54604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T17:18:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3ee81eb90d9e58d6